noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\twindow.google_analytics_uacct = \"UA-3380984-8\";\n</script>\n<div class=\"adsense\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\n\t\tgoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-7088061744296615\";\n\t\t/* CrawlWiki skyscraper */\n\t\tgoogle_ad_slot = \"8196155564\";\n\t\tgoogle_ad_width = 160;\n\t\tgoogle_ad_height = 600;\n-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Holy word</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f90; background-color: #fc6; border-left: 15px solid #f90; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.30\" title=\"0.30\">0.30</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<p><b>Holy word</b> is a damaging effect. When used against <a href=\"/Undead\" title=\"Undead\">undead</a> or <a href=\"/Demonic\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Demonic\">demonic</a> monsters, it deals <code>3d15 + (1d&lt;pow&gt; - 1) / 5</code><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> AC-ignoring damage and inflicts the <a href=\"/Daze\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Daze\">daze</a> status for 10-19 turns.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> When used against undead or <a href=\"/Demonspawn\" title=\"Demonspawn\">demonspawn</a> players, it halves HP instead. Unlike <a href=\"/Torment\" title=\"Torment\">torment</a>, this can kill you at 1 HP. Otherwise, it does nothing.\n</p><p>Holy word is a divine-only effect. It can be invoked from <a href=\"/The_Shining_One\" title=\"The Shining One\">The Shining One</a>'s weapon blessing and <a href=\"/Zin\" title=\"Zin\">Zin</a>'s Recite. <a href=\"/Nemelex\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Nemelex\">Nemelex</a> will use holy word exclusively on the player as <a href=\"/Torment_card\" title=\"Torment card\">punishment</a> (if you would be affected by it).\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>In <a href=\"/0.29\" title=\"0.29\">0.29</a>, the <a href=\"/Scroll_of_holy_word\" title=\"Scroll of holy word\">scroll of holy word</a>, the most common source of this effect, was removed.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.27\" title=\"0.27\">0.27</a>, Zin's Sanctuary caused a holy word effect.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.15\" title=\"0.15\">0.15</a>, holy word also <a href=\"/Cause_Fear\" title=\"Cause Fear\">scared</a> targets, and the <a href=\"/Good_god\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Good god\">good gods</a> made these scrolls more powerful for their followers.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The power is capped at 300. TSO's holy word has power = 100. Recite's power depends on piety and <a href=\"/Invocations\" title=\"Invocations\">Invocations</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.0/crawl-ref/source/spl-goditem.cc#L1016\">spl-goditem.cc:1016</a> (0.30.0)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.30.0/crawl-ref/source/spl-goditem.cc#L1036\">spl-goditem.cc:1036</a> (0.30.0)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916212933\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.064 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.115 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 85/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 284/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1203/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 99/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 4/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.000s\nLua virtual size: 8.02 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   85.978      1 -total\n 76.57%   65.837      1 Template:Version030\n 74.12%   63.727      1 Template:Version\n  3.68%    3.163      2 Template:Source_ref\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:3835-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916212933 and revision id 71898\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Holy_word&amp;oldid=71898\">http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Holy_word&amp;oldid=71898</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"><a h